title: Botany at Robertson Quay: Family-Friendly Dining
blurb: Culinary delights and mindful living come together.
description: Botany is a restaurant in Robertson Quay where culinary delights and mindful living come together. Founded in 2019 by Cassandra Riene, this all-day dining haven offers a diverse menu that caters to vegans, vegetarians, gluten-free diners, and meat lovers alike. Currently recognised as one of the best brunch places in Singapore, Botany combines delicious food with a welcoming ambiance. Whether you're looking for a relaxing weekend brunch or a memorable meal, we offer something for everyone. The restaurant provides a welcoming atmosphere for families and children.
address_display: 86 Robertson Quay, #01-03 Next to M Social Hotel, Singapore 238245
